videos.description: Kyle Kempt finds Allen Lazard in the end zone for a 14-yard score to give the Cyclones an early lead.
videos.headline: Iowa State strikes first with Lazard TD catch

videos.description: David Montgomery uses a stiff arm to break a tackle on his 22-yard touchdown run to extend Iowa State's lead.
videos.headline: Montgomery uses nice move in TD run for Iowa State

videos.description: Mason Rudolph takes his time and throws a spot on pass to Marcell Ateman in the back of the end zone for a 21-yard touchdown putting the Cowboys on the board.
videos.headline: Rudolph throws amazing pass for Cowboys TD

videos.description: Justice Hill rips off a powerful 9-yard run for a Cowboys touchdown to tie the game in the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State ties game with 9-yard TD

videos.description: Justice Hill powers through and breaks multiple tackles in a 52-yard run to put Oklahoma State on the 1-yard line.
videos.headline: Hill breaks multiple tackles in 52-yard run

videos.description: Justice Hill bounces off the defenders and finds the end zone for a 1-yard score to give the Cowboys the lead.
videos.headline: Hill finishes drive with short TD run

videos.description: Joel Lanning runs into the pile and pushes forward from the 1-yard line to tie the game before halftime.
videos.headline: Iowa State pushes pile to score before the half

videos.description: Iowa State head coach Matt Campbell says he likes what he saw from backup quarterback Zeb Noland on the final drive before the half.
videos.headline: Campbell impressed with Noland stepping up

videos.description: David Montgomery powers through from the 3-yard line to put the Cyclones in the lead.
videos.headline: Iowa State takes lead with short TD run

videos.description: Jalen McCleskey hauls in a pass from Mason Rudolph and runs 81 yards to set up an Oklahoma State touchdown.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State's McCleskey rips off 81-yard catch and run

videos.description: Justice Hill scores from the 1-yard line to put Oklahoma State back in the lead.
videos.headline: Hill scores 3rd touchdown for Cowboys

videos.description: Allen Lazard tips the ball to himself, makes a one-handed catch while staying in bounds to score the touchdown and give Iowa State the lead.
videos.headline: Lazard makes unreal one-handed catch

videos.description: David Montgomery breaks off his third touchdown run to extend the Cyclones' lead with over eight minutes left to play.
videos.headline: Montgomery extends Iowa State's lead in the 4th quarter

videos.description: Mason Rudolph has time and throws a perfect pass to Marcell Ateman for a 30-yard touchdown. Cowboys tie the game with the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Rudolph answers with perfect TD pass

videos.description: Mason Rudolph completes a 19-yard pass to Dillon Stoner to put Oklahoma State back in the lead late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Rudolph puts Oklahoma State back in the lead

videos.description: Marchie Murdock and A.J. Green both have a piece of the ball in the end zone, but it's ruled an interception for Green to seal the win for Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Iowa State's last gasp is picked off in the end zone

videos.description: Oklahoma State head coach Mike Gundy says he told his safeties to go up and catch the ball prior to the interception that sealed the Cowboys' 49-42 win.
videos.headline: Gundy predicted interception to the game
